Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/esra-ozturk/sync_folders.git


Move to the root directory and run :

Windows:
python main.py path_source path_replica synchronization_interval path_log_file

Linux/Ubuntu

python3 main.py path_source path_replica synchronization_interval path_log_file

Note that synchronization_interval is in minutes, e.g 1 . 
